00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,800
Science has a clearer story about ubiquitin proteasome than social media does.

2
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:08,800
This tiny protein is a master regulator in our cells.

3
00:00:08,800 --> 00:00:12,800
It tags unwanted proteins for destruction, ensuring balance and health.

4
00:00:12,800 --> 00:00:17,600
Disruption in this system can lead to diseases like cancer and neurodegeneration.

5
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:22,400
So, next time you hear about proteins, remember the unseen hero: ubiquitin.

